+
+## Edge Cases Generated
+
+| Case | Category | Status |
+|---|---|---|
+| `CASE_EDGE_001` | Base scatter below trigger boundary | EXECUTED |
+| `CASE_EDGE_002` | Base scatter above trigger boundary | EXECUTED |
